Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\xshad-4\fad(200,200)}时钟的指针分秒不停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\xshad-4\fad(200,200)}请不要留下我一人
